Reasons range from not enough time to just to hard.<br>
The whole thing hinges down to ONE thing.....Are you willing to devote just a few hours a week to completing it?  If so do it, if not move on and do something else.  Need one item to finish?  Find out who is in (insert whichever zone that one piece drops in) and ask them if you can come along.  Unless of course you or your guild has done something to piss whatever guild/group it is you are trying to tag along with you'll find most Raid Leaders will allow you to tag along.  <br>
<br>
Finishing the epic is a personal choice and listening to everyone else's pros and cons will just muddy the water even further.  Step up and make the choice. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.daveshirley.org/neil/mantriarodsig.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=yanbun>Yanbun</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master Summoner</span><br>  Posts: 584<br> <font color=#333333>(11/15/02 4:00:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7852.topic&index=22>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Maybe</span><hr size=1> Get the crown, sell the MQ of the entire epic <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showMessageRange?topicID=7852.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showPrevMessage?topicID=7852.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showNextMessage?topicID=7852.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7852.topic&index=22><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.threadControl?topicID=7852.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.g